  "body": "```\r\ncontract Storage {\r\n    struct S { uint x; }\r\n    S t;\r\n\r\n    function store(S storage x) internal {\r\n        S memory y = x;\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    function f() public {\r\n        store(t);   \r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nFunction `store` is considered `pure`. Same if `x` is used in function call conversion to memory. Reading members from `x` is properly detected.",
